1032
01:11:17,506 --> 01:11:19,440
Um, I...
[ bell tolls ]

1033
01:11:19,442 --> 01:11:20,775
Give me one second.

1034
01:11:20,777 --> 01:11:22,176
I have to use
the bathroom.

1035
01:11:22,178 --> 01:11:23,811
Be right back.

1036
01:11:29,184 --> 01:11:31,953
[ bell tolls ]

1037
01:11:32,921 --> 01:11:35,123
[ hurried footsteps ]

1038
