[ whispering ]
Shit, shit, shit, shit.

1039
01:11:43,599 --> 01:11:45,366
[ bell tolls ]

1040
01:11:45,368 --> 01:11:47,035
[ dialing cell phone ]

1041
01:11:51,206 --> 01:11:52,473
[ beeps ]

1042
01:11:53,642 --> 01:11:54,742
Come on, Trace.

1043
01:11:54,744 --> 01:11:56,711
[ line rings ]

1044
01:11:56,713 --> 01:11:59,647
[ hurried footsteps
