1045
01:11:59,649 --> 01:12:01,749
[ line rings ]

1046
01:12:01,751 --> 01:12:02,817
[ cell phone rings ]

1047
01:12:02,819 --> 01:12:04,385
[ line rings ]

1048
01:12:04,387 --> 01:12:05,420
[ cell phone rings ]

1049
01:12:05,422 --> 01:12:06,621
JIM: [ whispering ]
What the fuck?

1050
01:12:06,623 --> 01:12:07,889
[ line rings ]

1051
01:12:07,891 --> 01:12:10,091
Tracy!
[ cell phone rings,
