1052
01:12:12,027 --> 01:12:13,828
[ drums pounding ]

1053
01:12:13,830 --> 01:12:16,264
[ Aaron breathing nervously ]

1054
01:12:30,112 --> 01:12:32,880
AARON: Mithras
