as mask is placed ]

1056
01:12:52,302 --> 01:12:55,069
[ man speaks phrase
in foreign language ]

1057
01:12:55,071 --> 01:12:57,638
[ footsteps
withdrawing ]

1058
01:12:57,640 --> 01:12:59,741
AARON: Hello?

1059
01:12:59,743 --> 01:13:00,808
Hello?

1060
01:13:00,810 --> 01:13:03,211
[ breathing nervously ]

1061
01:13:03,213 --> 01:13:04,579
Hello?

1062
01:13:04,581 --> 01:13:07,014
[ panting ]

1063
01:13:12,721 --> 01:13:15,123
Guys? [ laughs ]

1064
01:13:22,564 --> 01:13:26,601
[ breathing nervously ]

1065
01:13:42,484 --> 01:13:48,389
[ horn sounding ]

1066
01:13:50,392 --> 01:13:51,859
[ man shouts
indistinctly ]

1067
01:13:51,861 --> 01:13:52,994
[ all shouting ]

1068
01:13:52,996 --> 01:13:54,362
AARON:
What the fuck?

1069
01:13:54,364 --> 01:13:55,363
No, no, no, no!

1070
01:13:55,365 --> 01:13:56,230
Wait, wait, wait!

1071
01:13:56,232 --> 01:13:57,865
Okay, wait!
Wait! I'm sorry!

1072
01:13:57,867 --> 01:13:59,500
I'm not a part of this!

1073
01:13:59,502 --> 01:14:00,868
I'm not a part of this!

1074
01:14:00,870 --> 01:14:01,969
[ men shouting ]

1075
01:14:01,971 --> 01:14:03,471
[ Aaron shouting ]

1076
01:14:03,473 --> 01:14:05,373
I'm sorry!

1077
01:14:05,375 --> 01:14:06,641
Help!

1078
01:14:06,643 --> 01:14:07,708
[ men shouting,
horns blowing ]

1079
01:14:07,710 --> 01:14:09,710
AARON: Oh, no!
I'll just go!

1080
01:14:09,712 --> 01:14:11,446
[ branches snapping ]

1081
01:14:11,448 --> 01:14:13,981
[ men shouting ]

1082
01:14:13,983 --> 01:14:18,019
[ horns blowing ]

1083
01:14:18,021 --> 01:14:20,321
[ knives clanking ]

1084
01:14:26,628 --> 01:14:28,062
[ Aaron groans, falls ]

1085
01:14:28,064 --> 01:14:29,630
[ silence, static ]

1086
01:14:29,632 --> 01:14:31,732
[ men shouting ]

1087
01:14:31,734 --> 01:14:34,202
MAN:
Brother! Down here!

1088
01:14:34,204 --> 01:14:36,204
[ horns blowing ]

1089
01:14:52,654 --> 01:14:55,089
[ Aaron panting ]

1090
01:15:00,128 --> 01:15:03,197
