1091
01:15:05,968 --> 01:15:08,302
[ Aaron breathing nervously ]

1092
01:15:16,211 --> 01:15:18,212
[ crickets chirping ]

1093
01:15:18,214 --> 01:15:21,415
[ Aaron breathing nervously ]

1094
01:15:46,642 --> 01:15:49,577
[ footsteps ]

1095
01:16:19,942 --> 01:16:21,709
[ silence ]

1096
01:16:23,645 --> 01:16:25,146
[ crickets chirping ]

1097
01:16:25,148 --> 01:16:27,815
[ Aaron breathing ]

1098
01:16:28,984 --> 01:16:31,285
[ footsteps ]

1099
01:16:50,105 --> 01:16:52,707
[ footsteps climb
to window ]

1100
01:16:52,709 --> 01:16:54,342
[ panting ]

1101
01:16:54,344 --> 01:16:56,510
[ whispering ] Oh, God.

1102
01:16:56,512 --> 01:16:57,712
My God.

1103
01:16:57,714 --> 01:16:58,946
Oh, my God.

1104
01:16:58,948 --> 01:17:00,681
[ running footsteps ]

1105
01:17:05,520 --> 01:17:06,520
Jim!

1106
01:17:06,522 --> 01:17:08,522
Aaron.

1107
01:17:08,524 --> 01:17:09,890
[ horn blows, men shouting ]

1108
01:17:09,892 --> 01:17:12,627
AARON: No!
No no no no no no!

1109
01:17:12,629 --> 01:17:14,128
[ knives clanging ]

1110
01:17:14,130 --> 01:17:17,465
[ Aaron whimpering ]

1111
01:17:17,467 --> 01:17:18,532
Aah!

1112
01:17:18,534 --> 01:17:20,568
Get the fuck
away from me!

1113
01:17:20,570 --> 01:17:22,703
[ men shouting,
knives slashing ]

1114
01:17:25,273 --> 01:17:31,045
[ intermittent static ]

1115
01:17:31,047 --> 01:17:33,347
[ silence ]

1116
01:17:34,716 --> 01:17:36,283
[ static ]

1117
01:17:36,285 --> 01:17:39,020
[ video rewinding ]

1118
01:17:39,022 --> 01:17:41,422
[ Aaron screams
in slow motion ]

1119
01:17:43,558 --> 01:17:45,126
[ men shouting ]

1120
01:17:45,994 --> 01:17:50,598
[ keyboard clicking ]

1121
01:17:58,774 --> 01:18:02,176
The core value
of the Tarsus Club is
communications--

1122
01:18:02,178 --> 01:18:04,412
communications
between governments,

1123
01:18:04,414 --> 01:18:06,580
businesses, individuals.

1124
01:18:06,582 --> 01:18:10,017
And, of course, we're
living in the golden age
of communications

1125
01:18:10,019 --> 01:18:11,452
because of globalization.

1126
01:18:14,623 --> 01:18:17,425
Unfortunately, with
the rise of the Internet,

1127
01:18:17,427 --> 01:18:19,293
there's a dark side
to globalization.

1128
01:18:19,295 --> 01:18:22,363
Essentially, that is
that anyone with a crazy idea

1129
01:18:22,365 --> 01:18:25,933
can communicate it
to millions of people
like a virus.

1130
01:18:25,935 --> 01:18:28,402
And the Tarsus Club has been
the target of these viruses,

1131
01:18:28,404 --> 01:18:31,405
including these
crazy conspiracy theories.

1132
01:18:31,407 --> 01:18:32,573
Well, actually,
it's become something

1133
01:18:32,575 --> 01:18:35,476
of a cottage industry,
I think,

1134
01:18:35,478 --> 01:18:37,178
within
conspiracy circles

1135
01:18:37,180 --> 01:18:39,647
to break in
to Tarsus meetings.

1136
01:18:39,649 --> 01:18:42,650
In fact, we've grown
so accustomed to it
over the years

1137
01:18:42,652 --> 01:18:46,320
that, uh,
it's almost become
part of the ritual

1138
01:18:46,322 --> 01:18:49,457
to scare people off
who try to break in.

1139
01:18:51,159 --> 01:18:54,128
JIM: I was
taken to a back room.

1140
01:18:54,130 --> 01:18:57,331
I was told
to let them know

1141
01:18:57,333 --> 01:18:59,600
where the rendezvous point
was with Aaron.

1142
01:18:59,602 --> 01:19:02,536
We were questioned
for a very long time,

1143
01:19:02,538 --> 01:19:06,841
but, uh, eventually
security let us go.

1144
01:19:06,843 --> 01:19:08,542
Even after Aaron realized

1145
01:19:08,544 --> 01:19:11,512
that they were
just scaring him,

1146
01:19:11,514 --> 01:19:14,315
he was still very upset.

1147
01:19:15,650 --> 01:19:19,520
I think Aaron
had been traumatized
by what had happened.

1148
01:19:19,522 --> 01:19:21,522
That was the last time
I saw him.

1149
01:19:26,962 --> 01:19:29,730
JENSEN:
To the people screaming
about conspiracy...

1150
01:19:32,300 --> 01:19:35,336
I'll let them in
on a little secret.

1151
01:19:36,204 --> 01:19:37,805
It's true.

1152
01:19:37,807 --> 01:19:41,242
Global leaders do
get together and collaborate.

1153
01:19:41,244 --> 01:19:44,445
Many of them, including
my boss, Murray Chance,

1154
01:19:44,447 --> 01:19:47,414
are working hard
to create a new world

1155
01:19:47,416 --> 01:19:49,250
where all nations
and all people

1156
01:19:49,252 --> 01:19:52,553
can come together
in one global community.

1157
01:19:54,055 --> 01:19:55,890
That's what it's all about,

1158
01:19:55,892 --> 01:19:59,894
the creation
of a single global community.

1159
01:20:01,163 --> 01:20:02,797
And if
that's a conspiracy...

1160
01:20:05,000 --> 01:20:10,538
If that's a conspiracy,
well, then, yes, we're guilty.

1161
01:20:13,074 --> 01:20:14,708
Hi, bud.

1162
01:20:19,080 --> 01:20:20,447
NICOLE:
Just for the record,

1163
01:20:20,449 --> 01:20:23,551
where do you think
Aaron went?

1164
01:20:27,522 --> 01:20:29,590
JIM:
I guess he ended up...

1165
01:20:34,029 --> 01:20:37,031
in the same place
Terrance did, didn't he?

1166
01:20:42,771 --> 01:20:44,872
And I just hope
wherever they are,

1167
01:20:44,874 --> 01:20:46,574
they both feel free.

1168
01:21:00,255 --> 01:21:03,524
[ ominous music ]

1169
01:23:33,141 --> 01:23:35,776
[ discordant horns blowing ]

